graph TD
    A[Windows Boot] --> B[Task Scheduler]
    B -->|Run as SYSTEM| C[Service EXE]
    C --> D{Lock exists?}
    D -->|No| E[Acquire Lock]
    D -->|Yes| F[Wait 30s]
    E --> G[Start Scheduler]
    G --> H[Run Scheduled Backups]
    H --> I[Release Lock on Exit]
    
    subgraph Service Control
        C --> J[SCM: Start Service]
        J --> K[Service Main Loop]
        K --> L[Check Lock]
        L -->|Stale| M[Take Over]
        L -->|Valid| N[Wait]
    end
